metadata.name: Metatriad #1
metadata.description:
Meta Triads NFT makes you a pioneer in digital wearables. The project unites all 3: Real life, Metaverse & AR worlds. Every holder gets following benefits:

- Tria Tokens 
- Access to DAO/Tribunal
- Breeding
- Access to limited collections
- Ownership of the Marketplace
  
Triads are creating a platform that will help apparel industry migrate into the metaverse. Eventually Triads Marketplace will become a main platform for creating and selling digital wearables.
